OL,6,FI was diagnosed with Behcet's disease
OL,7,Fin 2013, a rare disorder that causes
OL,8,Fblood vessel inflammation throughout
OL,9,Fyour body.
OL,11,FThere's also a neurological side, which
OL,12,Ffor me is things like seizures and has
OL,13,Fgiven me enteric neuropathy, where the
OL,14,Fgut stops functioning due to
OL,15,Fdegradation of the nerves and muscles.
OL,16,FThis is why I have the bowel issues and
OL,17,Fgastroparesis, a chronic condition
OL,18,Fwhere the stomach cannot empty in the
OL,19,Fnormal way.
